@NODE Shareware "RB2Exe Guide    Copyright © 2000 by Andreas Falkenhahn"
@{b}Shareware@{ub}

    RB2Exe is a Shareware program. However, it's not expensive for you
    to get the full version. The Shareware version is fully functional,
    except that the generated executable blocks the system for some time.

    See @{"here" link Registration} for details on how you can register RB2Exe!

@ENDNODE

@NODE Registration "RB2Exe Guide    Copyright © 2000 by Andreas Falkenhahn"
@{b}Registration@{ub}

    Registering isn`t expensive at all: Everyone can afford it! There
    are three different methods of registering:

    Method 1: Registration for private use only. The executables RB2Exe
              generates may be used on your computer only. You aren't
              allowed to spread them. Registration costs: $6 US/10 DM.

    Method 2: Private distribution licence. You may spread the generated
              executables as you want, but only for non commercial use. 
              Registration costs: $12 US/20 DM.

    Method 3: Commercial distribution licence. You may spread the
              generated executables as you want, also commercially!  
              Registration costs: $30 US/50 DM. 

    The commercial distribution licence (method 3) is only valid for
    one year. After that year the licence has to be refreshed. All other
    methods can be used for good.
 
    If you`ve decided which way of registration you are going to take,
    print the @{"Registration form" link Formular}, fill it out, put it
    in an envelope with the money and send it to:

    Andreas Falkenhahn
    An der Trift 2
    36132 Eiterfeld-Arzell
    GERMANY

    After I`ve received your registration I`ll immediately send you
    your personal RB2Exe full version!
    

    Some additional information:

    - If you haven`t got a printer you may also send the money without
      the @{"Registration form" link Form} but only if you really haven`t
      got any possibility to print it out! But don`t forget to note if
      you want the full version per e-mail or snail mail then! And don`t
      forget your address and signature!

    - Other forms of payment that I accept: Postal money order and Euro
      cheque. I do not accept international money orders or cheques!

    - Please don`t send me money in any exotic currencies which I can`t
      transfer to my bank account! Please send DM (Deutsche Mark) and
      US-Dollar only. Thank you.
 
@ENDNODE    
   
